CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 21, 1953, pg. 2 reads: "Charm Clinic Speaker - Mrs. Marian Jordon, executive secretary of the local branch o f the NAACP, discussed "Business Etiquette" at the fourth session of the Charm Clinic at the Kay Boys' Club Wednesday. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Marian Bond Jordon wearing light colored short sleeved sweater and square patterned neck scarf, posed in front of light colored wall, possibly in Kay Boy's Club
